                    <p class="card-text">Full Stack apprentice focused to php + laravel, but used to much more. DevOps is also a part of my skillset, like docker and aws</p>
                    <a href="https://github.com/feliperamoss" class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-sm me-2">GitHub</a>
                    <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/mehrullohb" class="btn btn-outline-info btn-sm">LinkedIn</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-4">
